# 🧩 Kanban Dashboard

## 🔥 WIP atual em Doing

```markdown
TABLE WITHOUT ID
text AS "Tarefa",
kanban_prioridade AS "Prioridade",
kanban_due AS "Prazo",
kanban_pedido AS "Pedido",
kanban_macrotarefa AS "Macrotarefa"
FROM "Kanban"
FLATTEN file.tasks AS T
WHERE !T.completed
AND T.kanban_status = "doing"
SORT T.kanban_prioridade DESC, T.kanban_due ASC
```
## 📌 Backlog

TASK  
FROM "Kanban"  
WHERE !completed  
AND kanban_status = "backlog"  
SORT kanban_prioridade DESC, kanban_due ASC

## 🚧 Doing

TASK  
FROM "Kanban"  
WHERE !completed  
AND kanban_status = "doing"  
SORT kanban_prioridade DESC, kanban_due ASC

## ⛔ Blocked

TASK  
FROM "Kanban"  
WHERE !completed  
AND kanban_status = "blocked"  
SORT kanban_prioridade DESC, kanban_due ASC

## ✅ Done (últimas 20)

TASK  
FROM "Kanban"  
WHERE completed  
OR kanban_status = "done"  
SORT file.name DESC  
LIMIT 20

  
